headline: 3 Reasons UPS is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, United Parcel Service’s shares (currently trading at $110) have posted a disappointing 17.5% loss while the S&P 500 was down 1.7%. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
